n所以，而家唔再係反送中，而係一系列逆權運動。"},{"pid":"4c4bb049ff64f151bbacef0d21a86f4fc4db1e87","tid":1374740,"uid":274756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"最後我想加多句，革命時代已經來臨，但唔會一朝一夕就會成功。呢個係一個開始，路還很長，不要洩氣，我地加油啦好嗎？"},{"pid":"58854948a32a5370a3029fa0fcf250431d305820","tid":1374740,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"因為1.警察同黑社會比之前更明目張膽 2.人人係記者，可以live &amp; 拍片"},{"pid":"5e3445d7436ea56516d370dfccc105a92ebf5b5f","tid":1374740,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5276045d7963cd651567ce194a2236d173eb5453","tid":1374740,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"$$"}]}